Product Description

24 inch 7 Speed Foldable Adult Tricycle
The frame of this k folding trike is made of carbon steel and can support a total weight of 110 kg (220 lbs) for rider and cargo. 24'' wheels are stable and practical. With its seven-speed drivetrain, double brakes, adjustable padded seat and practical large basket, it is perfect for picnics, shopping, leisure and more.

Load Capacity: 110kg/220lbs(rider and cargo combined)

Height of the Saddle: 85-98cm/33x38.5in
Fold Dimensions (L* W* H): 115x76x105cm/45x30x41in

Package Content

1 x Adult Tricycle
1 x Bicycle Pump
